    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1921-12-27T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1921-12-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="793"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d793">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.48/1885</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chief of the Division of Russian Affairs, Department of
                        State</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Poole</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-12-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 27, 1921</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Mr. Secretary</hi>: The Russian Ambassador called this
                    morning “to express formally his deep appreciation and gratitude” for the
                    Russian relief measure which has just passed Congress.<note n="29"
                        xml:id="d793fn29">See Executive Order No. 3601, Dec 24, <hi rend="italic"
                            >supra</hi>.</note> He said that he was convinced that it would assist
                    the recovery of Russia in every way.</p>
                <p>The Ambassador asked me to convey the foregoing to you, and expressed the hope
                    that you might find it convenient to convey it also to the President.</p>
                <p>Respectfully,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">D. C. Poole</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
